Tool = script.Parent
local stillEquipped = false
function onEquippedLocal(mouse) stillEquipped = true if mouse == nil then print("Mouse not found") return end while stillEquipped do print("Setting Mouse to go") mouse.Icon = "rbxasset://textures\\GunCursor.png" while Tool.Enabled and stillEquipped do wait(0.01) end print("Setting Mouse to wait") mouse.Icon = "rbxasset://textures\\GunWaitCursor.png" while not Tool.Enabled and stillEquipped do wait(0.01) end end end
function onUnequippedLocal() stillEquipped = false end
Tool.Equipped:connect(onEquippedLocal) Tool.Unequipped:connect(onUnequippedLocal)

-- Beware the Snakes! --
local Tool = script.Parent local Crate = Tool.Handle local vCharacter
local crateClone local numberOfSnakes = 6
local crateSound
local debris = game:GetService("Debris")
local smoke = Instance.new("Smoke") smoke.Opacity = 0.0 --smoke.RiseVelocity = 1.0 --smoke.Size = 10.0 smoke.Name = "CrateSmoke"
local count = 1
Tool.Enabled = true local crateAOE = Vector3.new(20.0, 20.0, 20.0)
Snake = Instance.new("Part") Snake.Size = Vector3.new(2.8, 0.8, 0.2) Snake.Transparency = 0.0 Snake.Shape = "Block" Snake.FormFactor = 3 Snake.Name ="SC" --Snake.CanCollide = true
local SnakeMesh = Instance.new("SpecialMesh") SnakeMesh.MeshType = "FileMesh" SnakeMesh.Name = "Mesh" SnakeMesh.MeshId = "http://www.roblox.com/asset/?id=49046138" SnakeMesh.TextureId = "http://www.roblox.com/asset/?id=49046409" SnakeMesh.Scale = Vector3.new(0.5, 0.5, 0.5) SnakeMesh.Parent = Snake
--Snake.CFrame = Snake.CFrame * CFrame.Angles(math.pi/2, 0.0, math.pi)
bodyVelocity = Instance.new("BodyVelocity") bodyVelocity.P = 10000 bodyVelocity.maxForce = Vector3.new(bodyVelocity.P, 0.0, bodyVelocity.P)
bodyGyro = Instance.new("BodyGyro") bodyGyro.P = 500000 bodyGyro.maxTorque = Vector3.new(bodyGyro.P, bodyGyro.P, bodyGyro.P)
function blast(crate, hit) if count > 0 then count = 0 vCharacter = Tool.Parent vPlayer = game.Players:GetPlayerFromCharacter(vCharacter) if vCharacter == nil then print("No Character") return end smokeClone = Instance.new("Smoke") smokeClone.Color = Color3.new(0.0, 0.0, 0.0) smokeClone.Size = 2.0 print("Creating Smoke") smokeClone.Parent = crate parts = game.Workspace:FindPartsInRegion3(Region3.new(crate.Position - crateAOE, crate.Position + crateAOE), vCharacter, 100) for i = 1, #parts do char = parts[i].Parent if char:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") ~= nil then if numberOfSnakes > 0 then snakeClone = Snake:Clone() snakeClone.CFrame = snakeClone.CFrame * CFrame.Angles(math.pi/2.0 , 0.0, math.pi/2.0) snakeClone.CanCollide = false snakeClone.Position = crate.Position - Vector3.new(0.0, 0.0, 0.0) snakeBV = bodyVelocity:Clone()
snakeBV.velocity = Vector3.new(parts[i].Position.X - snakeClone.Position.X, 0.0, parts[i].Position.Z - snakeClone.Position.Z).unit * 10.0 snakeBV.Parent = snakeClone snakeBV.Name = "snakeBV" snakeBG = bodyGyro:Clone() snakeBG.cframe = CFrame.new(snakeClone.Position, parts[i].Position) * CFrame.Angles(math.pi/2.0, math.pi, -math.pi/2.0) snakeBG.Parent = snakeClone snakeBG.Name = "BG" snakeClone.Parent = game.Workspace creatorTag = Instance.new("ObjectValue") creatorTag.Name = "creator" creatorTag.Value = vPlayer creatorTag.Parent = snakeClone newScript = Tool.InsertScript:Clone() newScript.Disabled = false newScript.Parent = snakeClone debris:addItem(snakeClone) numberOfSnakes = numberOfSnakes - 1 end end end --if crate then crate:Remove() end end end
function throw(crate, direction)
vCharacter = Tool.Parent if vCharacter == nil or vCharacter:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") == nil then return end
local spawnPos = vCharacter.Head.Position spawnPos = spawnPos + direction.unit * 5.0
crate.CFrame = CFrame.new(spawnPos, spawnPos + direction) crate.Parent = game.Workspace crate.Name = "Crate" crate.Velocity = direction * 20.0
crateFloat = Instance.new("BodyForce") crateFloat.force = Vector3.new(0.0, 98.1 * crate:GetMass(), 0.0) crateFloat.Parent = crate
crate.Touched:connect(function(hit) blast(crate, hit) end) co = coroutine.create(remove) coroutine.resume(co, crate)
end
function onActivated() if Tool.Enabled == false then return end
Tool.Enabled = false
vCharacter = Tool.Parent myHumanoid = vCharacter:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") if myHumanoid == nil then return end
myTorso = vCharacter:FindFirstChild("Torso") if myTorso == nil then return end
local target = myHumanoid.TargetPoint local direction = (target - vCharacter.Head.Position).unit
crateSound = Tool:FindFirstChild("CrateSound")
crateClone = Crate:Clone() crateClone.CanCollide = true
Crate.Transparency = 1.0 throw(crateClone, direction) wait(0.3) if crateSound then crateSound:Play() end
wait(5.7) Tool.Enabled = true Crate.Transparency = 0.0 numberOfSnakes = 6 count = 1 end
function onEquipped() end
function onUnequipped() if crateSound then crateSound:Stop() end if crate then crate:Remove() end end
function remove(crate) wait(3.0) if crate then crate.Velocity = Vector3.new(0.0, 0.0, 0.0) end --wait(2.0) if crate then crate:Remove() end end
Tool.Activated:connect(onActivated) Tool.Equipped:connect(onEquipped) Tool.Unequipped:connect(onUnequipped)

local Snake = script.Parent
bodyForce = Instance.new("BodyForce") bodyForce.force = Vector3.new(0.0, 196.1 * Snake:GetMass(), 0.0) bodyForce.Parent = Snake
local perpVelocity local sign = 1
function onTouch(hit) humanoid = hit.Parent:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") if humanoid ~= nil then tag = Snake:FindFirstChild("creator") if tag then tag.Parent = humanoid end humanoid:TakeDamage(8) snakeBV = Snake:FindFirstChild("SnakeBV") if snakeBV then snakeBV:Remove() end newScript = script:FindFirstChild("PoisonScript") if newScript and humanoid:FindFirstChild("PoisonScript") == nil then newScript.Parent = humanoid newScript.Disabled = false end
wait(1.0) if humanoid then tag = humanoid:FindFirstChild("creator") end if tag then tag:Remove() end if Snake then Snake:Remove() end end end
Snake.Touched:connect(onTouch)
snakeVelocity = Snake:FindFirstChild("snakeBV").velocity print("SnakeVelocity") if snakeVelocity then print("Perp Velocity") perpVelocity = snakeVelocity.unit:Cross(Vector3.new(0, 1, 0)) end
while Snake do snakeVelocity = Snake:FindFirstChild("snakeBV") if sign == -1 then snakeVelocity.velocity = snakeVelocity.velocity + (perpVelocity * 3.0 * sign) else snakeVelocity.velocity = snakeVelocity.velocity + (perpVelocity * 1.5 * sign) end sign = sign * -1 wait(1.0) end

humanoid = script.Parent
if humanoid then for i = 1, 15 do if humanoid.Health > 0 then humanoid:TakeDamage(6) end wait(1.0) end end
wait(2.0) script:Remove()
